<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وأَسْفَرَتِ المرأةُ:</span> كَشَفَتْ نِقابها.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>